HM=/711x513/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/36ICOEKMHVD5TERJI26LSF3V6E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxMrMeo_paw2ANThCvp5nkVwZeHM%3D%2F711x513%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F36ICOEKMHVD5TERJI26LSF3V6E.jpg&h=025ac17d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n麥劍秋80年代曾主持《K-100》。（網上截圖）"},{"pid":"48bc7dca87a00223c05a6c0fe901ba808f153c49","tid":2356886,"uid":292362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T05:38:29.000Z","msg":"Noted <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06c76a885103f3a708b83c3e9532d9b34f0df05b","tid":2356886,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T05:42:14.000Z","msg":"好耐冇睇cctvb都記得佢把聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa2ca0c42871508eb09d56cd82b9a1f007095b2","tid":2356886,"uid":24160,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T05:48:45.000Z","msg":"乜唔係羅山咩?"},{"pid":"f8375b8e5ddd7e252981326e43a66055a2c96db2","tid":2356886,"uid":235152,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T05:50:03.000Z","msg":"窮到向幕後狂開刀黃藍都中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a193ee564f8c257822cbb9609315f193cdff95cf","tid":2356886,"uid":89641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8375b8e5ddd7e252981326e43a66055a2c96db2","tid":2356886,"uid":235152,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T05:50:03.000Z","msg":"窮到向幕後狂開刀黃藍都中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T05:52:49.000Z","msg":"咁多年舊約老員工老臣子, 人工一定高, D大陸管理狗一定當佢眼中釘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6d03d6035967a838a2f30cf2d6045e1251992b0","tid":2356886,"uid":1082,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0aa2ca0c